Maintainer: Unknown <unknown@unknown>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), dkms, dh-dkms
Standards-Version: 4.5.0

Package: rtl8851bu-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: linux-headers-generic | linux-headers-amd64
Description: DKMS source for Realtek RTL8851BU USB WiFi 6 driver
 This package provides the source for the 8851bu kernel module for
 Realtek RTL8851BU/RTL8831BU USB WiFi 6 adapters. The module is built
 automatically when the package is installed or when the kernel is
 updated (via DKMS).
